track.name: One More Time
comments: It's the "Guns Of Brixton" of Sandinista and it's glorious.
Daft Punk got nothing on this.
Cuz it's one more time in the ghettoooo, one more time if you please. [2]
"don't  need no silicon to calculate poverty"  ...... amen Joe...........one more time!

Sandinista says this track FXXking Rocks, The Clash did Punk very well and their take on  white dub is just as good. A band that sounds timeless, lest we never forget how important they were in the history of music!!!!!
Yes, this and Washington Bullets are my favorites off of Sandinista! But I think I may like this one a bit more :)
